                        <span x-show="lang === 'en'">Safety Tech Hub</span>
                    </h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 text-base leading-relaxed">
                        <span x-show="lang === 'ko'">AI의 안전하고 책임 있는 작동을 위한 핵심 구조를 설계하고 검증하는 공간입니다.</span>
                        <span x-show="lang === 'en'">A space for designing and verifying core structures for safe and responsible AI operation.</span>
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-gray-800/40 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-700/50 hover:border-blue-500/50 transition-colors">
